I defined DeletionPolicy as Retain for a S3 bucket and realised that delete-stack behaves this bucket like a normal bucket without DeletionPolicy.
Then from aws console I found a discrepancy between the original template and processed template: DeletionPolicy was not there!
This is original template:
```
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: 2010-09-09
Description: Serverless backend for PM
Parameters:
  PMInboundBucketName:
    Default: com.v.test.inbound
    Description: Name of inbound bucket for PM objects
    Type: String
Resources:
  PMInboundBucket:
    DeletionPolicy: Retain
    Properties:
      BucketName:
        Ref: PMInboundBucketName
    Type: AWS::S3::Bucket
  PMProcessorFunction:
    Properties:
      CodeUri: s3://com.v.cloudformation.upload/98912aaadab31c003dfb1f6a70192945
      Description: PM processor
      Events:
        PMPublishEvent:
          Properties:
            Bucket:
              Ref: PMInboundBucket
            Events: s3:ObjectCreated:*
          Type: S3
      FunctionName: com-v-PM_PM-processor
      Handler: main.handler
      Runtime: python3.6
    Type: AWS::Serverless::Function
Transform: AWS::Serverless-2016-10-31
```

